            </p>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 mt-6">1. What are Cookies?</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
                Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They are widely used to
                make
                websites work more efficiently, as well as to provide information to the site owners.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 mt-6">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
                We use cookies to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                <li>Enhance your browsing experience.</li>
                <li>Analyze website traffic and performance.</li>
                <li>Personalize content and ads based on your preferences.</li>
                <li>Remember your login details and settings.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 mt-6">3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
                We use the following types of cookies:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                <li>
                    <strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> These are necessary for the website to function correctly, such
                    as
                    enabling you to log in or use e-commerce features.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Analytical/Performance Cookies:</strong> These help us understand how visitors interact with
                    our
                    website, enabling us to improve our services.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Functionality Cookies:</strong> These remember your preferences and help customize your
                    experience.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Advertising Cookies:</strong> These are used to deliver relevant advertisements to you based
                    on
                    your browsing behavior.
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 mt-6">4. Managing Cookies</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
                You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings. However, disabling cookies may affect
                your
                experience on our website.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
                For more information on managing cookies, please follow the instructions provided by your browser.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 mt-6">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
